title: 20 Nudes Dancers 20
description:
'20 Nude Dancers 20' Year One and Year Two

Tundra Publishing, 1990 and 91, 36 and 40 pages

Written and Illustrated by Mark Martin

Cartoonist Mark Martin's "20 Nude Dancers 20," was a long-running humor strip featured in Comics Buyer's Guide, a newsletter for comics collectors and fans. Largely autobiographical (though often with a hallucinatory, surreal twist), this hilarious strip pokes fun at the world of obsessive comics collectors, comics artists, conventions, and comics themselves.
